  "label::passcode_forgotten": "Requests for help with a forgotten app or account passcode (used to log in to the app, not to use the card). Deciding feature: if the user is locked out of the app or can’t log in because they don’t remember their passcode, select this; if the question is about the card’s PIN, select “get_physical_card.”",
